# (spuriously) reduce the first production above, we would find that we
# have a complete specifier_qualifier_list(type_name), hence a complete
# type name.

Up to this point, a type name has been recognized.
At this point, one of the following is expected:
  a type qualifier; or
  an abstract declarator; or
  a closing parenthesis ')'.

